    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/fco-legal-directorate"/>
    <title>FCO Legal Directorate Business Plan 2012 to 2013</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary/>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Foreign &amp;amp; Commonwealth Office’s (FCO) Legal Advisers provide advice to FCO Ministers and officials, including on questions of:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;International &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;EU &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Human Rights &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Constitutional law &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Law relating to the British Overseas Territories &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Domestic law (eg Freedom of Information Act and Data Protection Act)  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;To read more on the work of Legal Directorate see their Business Plan for 2012-13.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
