    <updated>2012-12-11T16:24:29+00:00</updated>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/human-rights"/>
    <title>Human rights</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary>Reports on FCO's recent activities to promote human rights abroad.</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The attached reports contain detailed information on the 
Foreign &amp;amp; Commonwealth Office’s activities to promote human rights abroad.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Each Report incorporates comments and recommendations that have been 
received over the course of the previous year from the House of Commons 
Foreign Affairs Committee and from a number of human rights 
non-governmental organisations.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The Reports are designed to be accessible to non-specialists with a general interest in foreign policy.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
