    <published>2011-12-16T00:00:00+00:00</published>
    <updated>2012-12-11T16:24:33+00:00</updated>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/fco-management-board-sub-committees"/>
    <title>FCO Management Board Sub-Committees</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary/>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Three sub-committees support the work of the FCO Board. They are: The Audit and Risk Committee - assists the Board on issues of risk, control and governance. The HR Committee - provides a corporate view of the FCO’s
HR policies and operations. The Operations Committee - ensures that network changes and efficiency savings are timely and coordinated.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
